15... Qf6+
{ The Queen stands better on f6 than on e7, and I want to make this move at a moment when White cannot ignore it. If Black had started with Be6, then after Rd4, Qf6 would not threaten anything. But if White tries Rd4 here, the Bishop will come to f5 instead. }
